{"tid":2063852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(超多J圖) TBB 梁茵話無同過著名傳銷公司亮碧思高層拍拖，大家點睇?","createTime":"2020-06-14T10:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T02:30:53.000Z","uid":121213,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"77e2e072e1e9cadf14b296d617c9e70b4e989ce6","tid":2063852,"uid":121213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T10:41:34.000Z","msg":"首先，我想賣吓以下廣告。<br />\n全港最大反傳銷亮碧思大聯盟Telegram谷上線喇，歡迎撚狗畀料爆料加入<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/becareful_LB_Laminated_marketing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbecareful_LB_Laminated_marketing&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=3d8a08c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/becareful_LB_Laminated_marketing</a><br />\n<br />\n事件的開始: TBB 女偽人疑似加入傳銷行業亮碧思資料整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2049483/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2049483/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O91DSoY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO91DSoY.jpg&h=b0f29bcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n留意返，梁茵好明顯係想同 Marshal 割蓆，根本唔係佢鐘意嘅類型，但事實又係咪咁呢? 無拍拖又同人哋屋企去旅行? 無拍拖又同人哋企到咁埋? 唔通你係PTGF ? 唔知收費幾多呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5DX33xm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5DX33xm.jpg&h=0f51894f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果真係無關係又點會同人哋老豆老母去旅行? 仲要貼到咁埋影相?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sE9Fmje.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsE9Fmje.jpg&h=a130f5e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇吓梁茵同 Marshal 屋企人去日本旅行幾開針?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AVwTGju.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAVwTGju.jpg&h=e9490439&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BarXoxV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBarXoxV.jpg&h=d4de6324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z8QX7ZB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz8QX7ZB.jpg&h=53d45e7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ndftvc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fndftvc2.jpg&h=0c772a9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔係佢鍾意嘅類型又成日去人哋「傳銷公司」嘅聯誼聚會? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gd4xWTh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGd4xWTh.jpg&h=9b36d1a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最搞笑梁茵講到 Marshal 婚宴出面等，但佢又可以坐低摸埋酒杯底啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DgZxWTp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDgZxWTp.jpg&h=34a00d34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺出面等都可以同你企埋一齊影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50iVUFb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50iVUFb.jpg&h=3839a297&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L7g8vdw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL7g8vdw.jpg&h=d6d6ab53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實好簡單，做生意係雙方，點解你會形容介紹朋友畀黃先生呢個動作係可以理解為一門生意? 難道做完呢單「生意」你有回佣收? 即係你除咗做TBB 仲有秘撈其他「生意仔」?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後,再加幾張傳銷mk妹J圖,益下D cd-rom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2cyOvfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum